    <summary>The best DaVinci Resolve companion app on Linux</summary>

    

    <!-- -->
    <!-- -->
    <description>

        <p>This app is created with the purpose of making it easier for Linux users to install and use DaVinci Resolve.</p>
        <p>Features :</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Automatic and dynamic dependecies installation</li>
            <li>DaVinci Resolve installation wizard easy start</li>
            <li>Application of post install patch</li>
            <li>Easy GPU Driver installation</li>
        </ul>

